title: Photostat, "The Rise of Rome: Head of a Man Facing Front, Scipio Afric", 1930–32
description: This photostat duplicates the view of a man in the drawing 1956-47-30. In the present object, however, the details of the orginal, such as the heavy shading and the thin dark lines of the mouth and eyebrows, are less apparent.

tombstone.epitaph:
Photostat, "The Rise of Rome: Head of a Man Facing Front, Scipio Afric", 1930–32.
1930–32. 34 x 34 cm (13 1/2 x 13 1/2 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-68.
